\v 32 e'tane ekama uya …®p…®'nokon; …®n Č' r…® t Čno'p Č nonkayai'ne', iyekumasa' pen n…® e'tane uya tekumasen pe iyesi emapu't…® m…®r…®, m…®r…® awonsi'k…® …®n Č' r…® inonkasa' r Č'p Č mari'mayai'ne', ekuma pe iyesi m…®r…®.\x - \xo 5:32 \xt 1 Koren 7:10-11\x*
